column5: Havent posted in a while, been quite busy, thought I would post up some pics from my last 2 outings, whities, lakers, ling and perch.
Nice man! Thats a sweet variety!
Nice haul of fish!  That's awesome!  We're heading to Simcoe Tuesday for 2 days.  Hopefully the jumbos will cooperate.
WOW nice  Ron. Hope to hook up next month with ya again dude.
Nice dark lakers.  Good stuff man!
Thanks for the kind words guys, definitely off to a solid start this season!
a good-sized daytime ling on plastics! You don't see that too often
Ya, the day after we got another one same size on a williams spoon, weird this year, we usually get them oftwn but only set lining, not often on lures.
